<h3 class="date"><a href="/2007/apr/02/">&#x27a0;</a> April 2, 2007</h3>


<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">


    
    <div class="well" id="apple-drm-free-itunes" >

        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://www.apple.com/pr/library/2007/04/02itunes.html">Apple Unveils Higher Quality DRM-Free Music on the iTunes Store</a></h4>

        
            
        

        <p>Apple will be selling DRM-free music from EMI next month.  Pitched as &#8220;higher-quality&#8221; (256kbps AAC) to justify the price increase.  The interesting statistic once this launches is going to be the number of people who choose the lower-cost DRMed version.</p>

