<h3 class="date"><a href="/2007/mar/23/">&#x27a0;</a> March 23, 2007</h3>


<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">


    
    <div class="well" id="xvid-working-appletv" >

        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://forums.somethingawful.com/showthread.php?s=&amp;threadid=2391956">We just got xvid working on the Apple TV</a></h4>

        
            
        

