    <div class="well" id="apple-thoughts-music" >

        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://www.apple.com/hotnews/thoughtsonmusic/">Apple - Thoughts on Music</a></h4>

        
            
        

        <p>Steve Jobs publicly calls for the record companies to drop their requirement for DRM on online music sales: &#8220;Imagine a world where every online store sells DRM-free music encoded in open licensable formats. [&#8230;] This is clearly the best alternative for consumers, and Apple would embrace it in a heartbeat.&#8221;</p>

